{
  "panel_1": [
    {
      "id": "1cee8f32-a46b-4721-b33d-d40399eaf5e2",
      "text": "# The Shield and the Crowned Heaven",
      "created": 1777152910099,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5f5110b-6b30-4a2d-a068-c9468ffa241d",
      "text": "First of all he formed a shield, both large and solid, adorning it all over.",
      "created": 1777152910099,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7544db85-68d4-486e-b33b-8ff322c9507b",
      "text": "Around it he threw a shining border, triple, glittering, and a silver belt.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5f25390b-4313-4af0-a212-e370af02b881",
      "text": "Five folds made the shield itself, and on it he formed many ornaments with cunning skill.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f30b69dd-8184-4f80-87c6-8925c4502e81",
      "text": "> On it he wrought the earth, and the heaven, and the sea.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "a39859ab-318f-42b9-bdfc-e09fc0bde0c4",
      "text": "He wrought the unwearied sun, the full moon, and all constellations.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ae06742e-41c1-4230-939a-479ef11362f7",
      "text": "The Pleiades and the Hyades were there, and the might of Orion.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "9157b317-b586-4f81-ba22-7b3e11ab445c",
      "text": "The Bear, also called the Wain, revolves there and watches Orion.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ffb73599-ff25-443f-b83a-39378e49b8c1",
      "text": "The Bear alone is without a share of the baths of the ocean.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "99406b2d-71f2-4ce0-a89e-6d7b48b1b9c6",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "333e49da-cfb3-48f1-b6dc-0466a9a6ae11",
      "text": "Within the shield, cities, armies, field, vineyard, oxen, dance, and Oceanus wait.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "36492169-0b4d-4cb7-9770-f7d41515b08c",
      "text": "Gold, tin, silver, brass, blood, grapes, and river-light become one moving world.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_2": [
    {
      "id": "fc490d65-e9b7-4d77-9e94-6194354d95ca",
      "text": "# The City of Marriage, Feast, and Judgment",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "310cac59-f255-4d29-9c36-bd7500f8c49d",
      "text": "On it also he fashioned two beautiful cities of articulate-speaking men.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e0f4bec1-3546-4ee8-b5bf-e1c4024197fc",
      "text": "In the one were marriages and feasts, bright under heaven like constellations.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "1f6a7c92-79db-4a1a-8ec9-4023e99ae5cb",
      "text": "They conducted the brides from their chambers through the city with brilliant torches.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8d0c6bcb-74af-477d-ad9a-dc2615293364",
      "text": "Many a bridal song was raised, while young men danced in a circle.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "647d5342-6a74-4fdc-aa46-11e8019a2708",
      "text": "Among them flutes and lyres gave forth their sounds beside the portals.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "b4077155-85eb-42f5-b4d3-86adb91257e3",
      "text": "The women standing, each at her portals, admired the dance and the city.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "cf15406e-202e-49b6-a9d7-455c8ccbddfe",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "002647f3-e186-4b2c-bdf8-cf761fd32ae0",
      "text": "But the people were assembled in the forum, for there a strife had arisen.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "23177287-ff63-48bc-8c05-c77270ff2d3f",
      "text": "Two men strove for the ransom-money of a slain man.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e01c769-1b76-4ad4-a431-626437c2a7c1",
      "text": "One affirmed that he had paid all, but the other denied that he had received any thing.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "1e94af4f-8f55-4965-a68f-f02fa310e472",
      "text": "Both wished to find a termination of the dispute before a judge.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7512847c-24e2-4136-b1e8-7b36a2cdc7e3",
      "text": "The heralds reined in the people, and the elders sat on polished stones.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "23bb9995-a9e5-4d32-a687-3a2cd0c98216",
      "text": "They sat in a sacred circle and held the staves of the loud-shouting heralds.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e0c20c2-5b0f-4c20-9de3-b84aa1a58a34",
      "text": "There lay in the midst two talents of gold for the judgment most correctly pronounced.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "816c6c0a-53ee-4a29-95c3-6b9ab03e9904",
      "text": "Even here, the shield holds Mars, Fate, gold, and law in the same bright border.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_3": [
    {
      "id": "68d47540-aea3-4b18-8cbc-a742fb940041",
      "text": "# The Besieged City, Ambush, and Battle",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "2fcc2782-ad17-4dd5-a36a-52fbeeefd252",
      "text": "Around the other city sat two armies of people, glittering in arms.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "cdb2c163-9a37-4412-be92-a47343bbb3fd",
      "text": "A plan was agreeable to them: destroy it entirely or divide all the wealth in two.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "edf9ba5c-db22-4d4a-a83b-38b8ff0f119c",
      "text": "The pleasant city did not yet obey, but was secretly arming for an ambush.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "545480d3-9c8d-4101-802e-d3cf96ae9f4f",
      "text": "Beloved wives and young children stood upon the wall guarding it.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "fb82c544-baf1-4b6f-a5d1-a516f5e4fee4",
      "text": "With them stood the men whom old age possessed.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "aa94cb3d-21c5-4a9a-80d1-5d8977cdb647",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "09e3ea48-5171-4ba3-a1af-6a1f8e0b0cda",
      "text": "Mars and Pallas Minerva led them, both golden and clad in golden garments.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "83a3b899-45d9-4c8f-95b4-178ba32bbf44",
      "text": "They reached a place fit to lay an ambush, by a river and watering-place.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "acc32fa3-8824-4a97-a4ad-79594741748e",
      "text": "There they settled, wrapped in shining brass, while two spies sat apart.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3f57baec-5fb7-45ea-9a1f-54f0afa33b7e",
      "text": "The spies watched for sheep and curvated oxen moving toward the river.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a6cdbd30-0432-4642-9196-eff296e36249",
      "text": "Two shepherds followed, amusing themselves with pipes, not foreseeing fraud.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f63dd542-17c4-456a-89da-c916fcb63ead",
      "text": "The ambushers slaughtered the herds of oxen and the fair flocks of sheep.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c6440f7-bce0-464e-b356-0cb2ca4ef366",
      "text": "They slew the shepherds besides, and the tumult among the oxen reached the councils.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "4467369f-4c3a-4182-9ee1-7c7a39f5ba0c",
      "text": "The besiegers mounted nimble-footed horses and pursued them to the banks of the river.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f77c8bc8-7c0b-4164-82a3-6c7eecf1ef36",
      "text": "There they fought a battle and wounded one another with brazen spears.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c346b49-03e1-4037-9e39-31d2ad3dcde5",
      "text": "Among them mingled Strife and Tumult, and destructive Fate.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "84d455a0-fc71-4cfb-bc7e-c890910e640e",
      "text": "Fate dragged one dead by the feet, and her garment was crimsoned with blood.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "07afed55-6ddb-4f63-a97a-8fd5ff4d57f9",
      "text": "They turned like living mortals, fought, and drew away slaughtered bodies.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_4": [
    {
      "id": "3d84bb6b-b466-4014-9576-c8f274176c7e",
      "text": "# The Fallow Field, Corn, Reapers, and Feast",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c4f87a6-9796-48de-9b93-b2582879838c",
      "text": "On it he placed a soft fallow field, rich glebe, wide, thrice-ploughed.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "73f1d94f-d28f-4514-a659-28c98542d423",
      "text": "Many ploughmen drove hither and thither, turning round their teams.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e577e51-abd3-4b44-9389-7f599b22430b",
      "text": "When they reached the end of the field, a man gave them very sweet wine.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "17c7fd0d-2ba9-488d-ace8-bce103dbfc8b",
      "text": "They turned themselves in series, eager to reach the other end of the deep fallow.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3c9a825d-a352-4584-860c-7c1469c9ea88",
      "text": "The field grew black behind, and was like ploughed land, though being golden.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "96b260ff-d003-49dd-bcdf-874419fca71c",
      "text": "This was a very great marvel within the shield.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "b734df98-dd20-4fa1-9186-212dd2eb8fa7",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "60bcc980-2b26-4361-8598-007dbfb3cd0f",
      "text": "There he also placed a field of deep corn, where reapers were reaping.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5eb9e8e2-dd44-4ba0-94cc-80d8a52a4313",
      "text": "Sharp sickles were in their hands, and handfuls fell thick along the furrow.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "4ee26d5b-d017-4105-861e-c936af191928",
      "text": "Binders of sheaves tied the corn with straw ropes in series.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d7f717b8-7eb4-4b10-bccd-dbd1692ee4c4",
      "text": "Boys gathered the handfuls and continually supplied the binders.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c522720-6b6a-48b5-9cb2-2fdb446710d0",
      "text": "Among them the king in silence stood over a furrow, rejoicing in his heart.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "80d8e57c-dbff-4965-97ad-3be912fb4cf0",
      "text": "Apostles apart, beneath an oak, prepared a feast after sacrificing a huge ox.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "290d9f70-c988-4af2-bfc8-bba99bef991f",
      "text": "Women strewed much white barley meal as a dinner for the reapers.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "378bfe10-e8e7-4d91-a34e-09d7aa15c220",
      "text": "The fallow field answers the forum, the river, the oxen, and the talents of gold.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_5": [
    {
      "id": "74782266-d04c-44e8-aacc-8de077ae1e00",
      "text": "# The Vineyard and the Linus Song",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "8bc3e75f-2c16-44f9-882a-eb81b76da2a5",
      "text": "On it also he placed a vineyard heavily laden with grapes, beautiful, golden.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ac9da21f-ff54-41bb-9793-c2dd830f04ea",
      "text": "The clusters throughout were black, and it was supported by silver poles.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8b2ca9bf-387e-48a3-a63c-d1722f8f1c8d",
      "text": "Around it he drew a dark-blue trench, and around it a hedge of tin.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "16992e79-5975-4f4a-a597-2440655f6d6b",
      "text": "There was but one path by which the gatherers went to collect the vintage.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ca8e2dc7-6b2f-4254-b7c6-e58d995706c3",
      "text": "Young virgins and youths of tender minds carried sweet fruit in woven baskets.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "08527eaa-1482-4677-95e5-3c9f8741ebc3",
      "text": "In the midst of them a boy played pleasantly on a shrill lyre.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "62a992f1-4a69-46ea-8c19-6cf33bb5804e",
      "text": "He sang the beautiful Linus song with a slender voice.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3a9ed60-3dcb-4699-96e4-fa5a8cb40979",
      "text": "They followed with singing and shouting, beating the ground, hopping with their feet.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d8018e10-c10d-4f84-a6b7-428b2822a0f9",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "2bd67e7e-8347-4fae-a97b-33a9cd7d022c",
      "text": "The vineyard repeats the dance, the bridal song, the gold, the tin, and the shield.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "83876072-35e3-4545-a339-617f4ac70afe",
      "text": "Its black grapes echo the black fallow field, blood-dark battle, and Oceanus border.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_6": [
    {
      "id": "3bbbe9c1-ae69-4dfb-9d0a-ab23dee8e847",
      "text": "# The Herds, Lions, Dogs, and Sheepfolds",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "7d5120f0-2446-43c8-8164-e94ed1e1e7d3",
      "text": "On it he fashioned a herd of lofty-horned oxen, made of gold and tin.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf8090be-42c0-471d-ad0c-0859dd8768f1",
      "text": "Lowing, the oxen rushed from the stall to the pasture beside a murmuring river.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "1da1ef11-24d4-4236-a902-64273bdfdef7",
      "text": "They moved along the waving reed, followed by four golden herdsmen.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "cadd603f-47c4-45f9-9b03-35d638fbc180",
      "text": "Nine dogs, swift of foot, followed the oxen into the pasture.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bfd660de-72f1-472f-95e8-9e46be61ee47",
      "text": "Two terrible lions among the foremost oxen seized a bellowing bull.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "938d494d-1f58-493d-bea9-457371cafdb6",
      "text": "The bull, dragging, roared loudly, while dogs and young men ran up to him.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "2eb80dc4-35c8-4092-8d83-937b6dcadee5",
      "text": "The lions tore the hide of the huge ox and devoured entrails and black blood.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "000a78c3-9bce-4e0c-bb75-129fbc964f08",
      "text": "The shepherds vainly pressed upon them, urging on the fleet dogs.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c513533b-2611-4df3-bccf-6caffb434f10",
      "text": "The dogs refused to bite the lions, but stood near, barking and flying them.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d2319b71-bb62-4c67-ab87-b41ad35c85bf",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "ed577b4a-6e61-4f67-9e38-c014574ceb95",
      "text": "On it also the illustrious Vulcan formed a large pasture of white sheep.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "818a7859-0b02-4cf2-9fec-c0c5f9cb6cfc",
      "text": "The sheep stood in a beautiful grove, with folds, covered sheds, and cottages.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "b0be5fcb-cb31-4e2c-93ed-cf8471e2035d",
      "text": "Here the river of ambush returns as pasture, and Fate returns as lions.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_7": [
    {
      "id": "4c8180f3-a830-4370-974f-16a348df96a1",
      "text": "# The Dance of Daedalus and the Border of Oceanus",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "e57f2f8c-1e8e-4e47-b29f-bce56629525e",
      "text": "On it also the illustrious Vulcan embellished a dance.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c71a0231-a19e-4587-b9e7-c53a39257528",
      "text": "It was like the dance in wide Gnossus that Daedalus composed for Ariadne.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "80358478-7819-48f3-afbf-3f7b5ee35af9",
      "text": "There youths and alluring virgins danced with hands on each other's wrists.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5377b8ba-9de3-4f30-9120-0864031d1ef3",
      "text": "The virgins had fine linen robes, and the youths wore well-woven tunics.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bda28438-42f6-4c68-b6c3-ee3d954669f1",
      "text": "The youths shone slightly with oil and carried golden swords from silver belts.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6714269a-0f8d-4724-8c42-83ec31a036bf",
      "text": "At one time they moved lightly with skilled feet, like a potter testing a wheel.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "344c79b0-47ac-4827-a6b9-e2051f023e34",
      "text": "At another time they moved in series towards each other.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6eecf884-019c-42e0-b5bc-7869f2502718",
      "text": "A large crowd stood around the enjoyable dance, delighted.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7fddcab7-ff59-46b4-82d7-00c8747239ec",
      "text": "Among them two tumblers, beginning their song, spun round in the midst.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c21e8219-3777-4500-8fe5-298cd993ede4",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e18a602-4746-4ef5-94c3-237fa402ef5a",
      "text": "In it he placed the vast strength of the river Oceanus.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "30175d2f-7634-454a-9483-570c129a8c0f",
      "text": "Oceanus ran around the extreme border of the well-formed shield.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3f70701-ff64-463b-9560-d40e41982c26",
      "text": "The shield closes where it began: circle, silver belt, dance, river, heaven, sea.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
